				Item Class
			</h3>
			<p class="mt-4">
				Contains information about what type of citizen it is. It can be changed using <Link
					classes=""
					href="https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=455068042"
					text="Asset ItemClass Changer by Snow_Cat"
					theme="externallink"
				/>.
			</p>
