				Filename
			</h3>
			<div class="flex flex-col gap-6 mt-4 lg:flex-row">
				<div class="lg:w-2/3">
					<p>
						The filename input is on the bottom left, this is what the actual file will be called. It's not
						recommended to use spaces, dots, or special symbols.
					</p>
				</div><div class="lg:w-1/3">
					<a href="/images/asset/citizen/citsave.jpg" target="_blank">
						<Picture
							width={images.citsave.width / 2}
							densities={[1.5, 2]}
							formats={['avif', 'webp']}
							src={images.citsave}
